ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
Immigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectMinister of Citizenship and Immigration with Provinces - Resettlement Assistance Program - ** Agreement*
PrecisOrder Approving that the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration ENTER INTO CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS with the Government of any PROVINCES with respect to the RESETTLEMENT ASSISTANCE PROGRAM, substantially in accordance with the a draft Agreement, in order to recognize the additional financial burden faced by these provinces in relation to irregular migration.
